ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 234, Saskatchewan
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 234 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of federal concern; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to SASKATCHEWAN with respect to the spring flood that occurred from April 25, 2020 to August 31, 2020.
